==Komol war blanetow erel==
Gwelys re beu komol war an brassa rann a blanetow yn [[System_howlek|Kevreyth an Howl]]. Komol tew stratiform dioksid sulfur yw an re war an planet [[Gwener_(planet)|Gwener]]. Komol noswolow, cirrus, cirrocumulus ha stratocumulus gwrys a rew dowr re beu gwelys war [[Meurth_(planet)|Veurth]].  Yma komol fest tew gwrys a ammonya, hidrosulfid ammoniom ha dowr war [[Yow_(planet)|Yow]] ha [[Sadorn_(planet)|Sadorn]], hag an keth eghennow gwrys a vethan war [[Ouran_(planet)|Ouran]] ha [[Nevyon-(planet)|Nevyon]]. Yma komol cirrus gwrys a vethan war loor Sadorn, [[Titan]].
